        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="how-to-start-the-service"><a href="#how-to-start-the-service" class="headerlink" title="how to start the service"></a>how to start the service</h1><h2 id="install-python-dependencies"><a href="#install-python-dependencies" class="headerlink" title="install python dependencies"></a>install python dependencies</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">pip <span class="token function">install</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-U</span> <span class="token parameter variable">-r</span> requirements.txt<span class="token builtin class-name">export</span> <span class="token assign-left variable"><span class="token environment constant">PATH</span></span><span class="token operator">=~</span>/.local/bin/:<span class="token environment constant">$PATH</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="setup-environment-or-use-my-env"><a href="#setup-environment-or-use-my-env" class="headerlink" title="setup environment, or use my .env"></a>setup environment, or use my .env</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">cp .env.prod .env# orcp &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;.env .env<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="start-the-service-you-might-need-to-update-port-to-avoid-conflict"><a href="#start-the-service-you-might-need-to-update-port-to-avoid-conflict" class="headerlink" title="start the service, you might need to update port to avoid conflict"></a>start the service, you might need to update port to avoid conflict</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">uvicorn app.app:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8002<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="when-testing-remotely"><a href="#when-testing-remotely" class="headerlink" title="when testing remotely"></a>when testing remotely</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">uvicorn app.app:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8002<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="calling-api-remotely-to-simulate-an-front-end"><a href="#calling-api-remotely-to-simulate-an-front-end" class="headerlink" title="calling api remotely to simulate an front-end"></a>calling api remotely to simulate an front-end</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none"># follow the above steps to start the service, you need to adjust certain variables like port and session id and otp_code to your own case when running the following tests.# sign in otpstart python3 interactive console:import requestsr &#x3D; requests.post(&#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:8000&#x2F;sign_in_otp&#39;, json&#x3D;&#123;&#39;phone_number&#39;: &#39;13912345678&#39;&#125;)r.content# confirm otpr &#x3D; requests.post(&#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:8000&#x2F;confirm_otp&#39;, json&#x3D;&#123;&#39;otp_code&#39;: &#39;53164&#39;, &#39;session_id&#39;: &#39;6ec3997d549dc36e39be883f9ce59884bd9a8fbe&#39;&#125;)r.contentheaders &#x3D; &#123;&#39;Authorization&#39;: &#39;eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6ImJhNmMxNjdlODg1ZWE0YmU4MjUyZmIwMWM2MWZjNTU0MzkwODlmMzg5ZWUxYjA1OTJmYzhjNGY0MTcxOTY0MDMiLCJleHAiOjE3Mzg3NzA2NzB9.q3JnU6OrcPKwzZ4coxURUljcbbWrWWrsyjQZ8oOf5dU&#39;&#125;r &#x3D; requests.post(&#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:8000&#x2F;user_info&#39;, json&#x3D;&#123;&#39;first_name&#39;: &#39;abc&#39;, &#39;last_name&#39;: &#39;def&#39;&#125;, headers&#x3D;headers)r.contentr &#x3D; requests.post(&#39;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:8000&#x2F;price&#39;, json&#x3D;&#123;&#39;seller&#39;: &#39;target&#39;, &#39;upc&#39;:&#39;673419376730&#39;&#125;)r.content<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
      
